  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat (400°F).",
    "Thread 1.5 pounds of flank steak onto skewers, leaving a little space between each piece.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together thyme, garlic powder, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Brush the mixture evenly onto both sides of the beef.",
    "Brush the nuka-pickle onto the beef, reserving any remaining for serving.",
    "Grill the skewers for 8-10 minutes per side, or until cooked to your desired level of doneness.",
    "Transfer the skewers to a plate and let rest for 5 minutes.",
    "Serve the beef skewers hot, garnished with chopped cilantro and lime wedges if desired.",
    "Slice the beef thinly against the grain before serving."
